# Cursor Style Test
# Tests bar cursor style with custom color
Output examples/svgs/cursor/prompt-emoji.svg

Set FontSize 16
Set Theme twilight
Set Title "Bar Cursor Style"

# Use bar cursor style with green color
Set CursorStyle bar
Set CursorColor #50fa7b
Set PromptPrefix "🧪"

Type "echo 'This uses a bar cursor'"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Type "echo 'with a custom green color'"
Enter
Type "echo 'and a emoji prompt prefix'"
Enter
Sleep 1s
